1. *Zamisli* da putuješ kroz vreme. (Imagine traveling through time.)
2. Ne mogu *zamisliti* da si uspeo da uradiš to sam. (I can't imagine you managed to do it on your own.)
3. Kada *zamislimo* koliko nas ima na ovoj planeti, osetimo se maleni. (When we imagine how many people there are on this planet, we feel small.)
4. *Zamisliš li* ikada kako bi bilo da pobegnemo zajedno? (Do you ever imagine what it would be like if we ran away together?)
5. Da li si ikada *zamislila* da postaneš poznata pevačica? (Have you ever imagined becoming a famous singer?)
6. Nije lako *zamisliti* kako bi svet izgledao bez tehnologije. (It's not easy to imagine what the world would look like without technology.)
7. Kada *zamisliš sebe* u budućnosti, šta vidiš? (When you imagine yourself in the future, what do you see?)
8. Mogu *zamisliti* koliko ćeš biti srećan kada ti dam ovaj poklon. (I can imagine how happy you'll be when I give you this gift.)
9. *Zamisli* da si sada na egzotičnoj plaži sa koktelom u ruci. (Imagine you're on an exotic beach right now with a cocktail in your hand.)
10. Uvek se *zamislim* kada slušam ovu pesmu. (I always get lost in thought when I listen to this song.)